5.1.What is Ubelix?
	Ubelix ist he high performance compunting cluster of UniBe. It is a Linux Cluster.

5.2. How do you gain access?
  The campus account must be activated by the Ubelix team. The request for activation can be submitted on the service desk.

5.3. How do you submit a job?
  The resurce manager is SLURM. A job can be submitted by sbatch (batch script), srun (directly running the executable) or salloc (interactive)

5.4. Who can have access?
  It is available for all personell oft he University for their scientific work. Students can have access if they need it for a coure or a thesis.

